{"tid":2137633,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"80後的士哥狂儲滙豐　每月收息淨袋過萬退休","createTime":"2020-08-03T05:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T04:53:59.000Z","uid":51920,"like":148,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"4f1ac6a0a8ad091685ffbda120122cc854e3a299","tid":2137633,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:29:24.000Z","msg":"近日香港討論區有一名33歲的士哥，以靠「一注獨贏儲滙控成功退休」，引起網民討論。<br />\n文：劉靜遠<br />\n<br />\n中銀香港手機開戶，提供7x24全天侯銀行服務！<br />\n這名的士哥表示，揸的士11年，過去每月開足30日工，每日揸12個鐘，一個月平均儲蓄17,500元，一夠錢就買滙控，「世紀供股時，手持5,200股，到2016年12月，終於買夠40,000股，每個月可收過萬元利息。」<br />\n<br />\n以滙控現價估計，的士哥手持滙控股份市值約260萬元，每年如可收6厘息，則共收息15.6萬元，相當於每個月有逾萬元收入。<br />\n<br />\n雖然有網民質疑「咁少錢就滿足了」，不過，的士哥自稱生活要求不高，與母親同住自置頹樓，日日打機、上網、睇書、打波，一個月花費幾千元，已經好開心。也有不少網民表示羨慕「喜歡工作便工作，放假便放假」的生活。"},{"pid":"c6d475d13e59c4521f15fe2e8befee23124da640","tid":2137633,"uid":51920,"like":175,"dislike":2,"score":173,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sYFB9nY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsYFB9nY.jpg&h=56fbb6c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86832b51c551f80ed71f8ddcdfccc0de735f3bb0","tid":2137633,"uid":124616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bb1896e8ebe0741dd4925f71ac80437d6d9a47","tid":2137633,"uid":21090,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:32:59.000Z","msg":"又要番工了"},{"pid":"5f8cadc0f44ae5214496fc51caaaf616438d0505","tid":2137633,"uid":139319,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"c6d475d13e59c4521f15fe2e8befee23124da640","tid":2137633,"uid":51920,"like":175,"dislike":2,"score":173,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sYFB9nY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsYFB9nY.jpg&h=56fbb6c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:34:22.000Z